=You are an expert sales copywriter. Generate a highly personalized cold outreach message based on the prospect's information.

**Prospect Details:**
- Name: {{ $json.first_name }} {{ $json.last_name }}
- Title: {{ $json.title }}
- Company: {{ $json.company }}
- Location: {{ $json.location }}

**Our Company:** {{ $('Set Campaign Variables').item.json.company_name }}
**Value Proposition:** {{ $('Set Campaign Variables').item.json.value_proposition }}

**Instructions:**
1. Start with a personalized opener that references their role or company
2. Clearly state the value proposition in one sentence
3. Include a soft call-to-action
4. Keep it under 100 words
5. Professional but conversational tone
6. No hype or pushy language

**Output Format:**
Provide ONLY the message body, no subject line or greetings. Return as JSON:
{
  "message": "your personalized message here"
}

